{
  "stem": "3360.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this is what they had been fed since the age of 10.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I don't know how much blame you can really attach to that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Those are the things that I always thought about that I still think about today.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Also, they were taught that-- and I heard this first-hand from them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because there was some who was still confiding in me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That if they hear their parents-- now, this was not in school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was if they were in the Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had their meetings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had their evenings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they did their marching and their singing, their camaraderie like stuff, which is fun, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I even hoped that-- I even kind of thought sometimes I'd like to be in it myself, except for this Jewish stuff.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how they got drawn in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That if their parents expressed themselves in saying something about Hitler or any of the top Nazis, that they are to report that as good German children.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are to report that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was not an unusual thing that people would heard the doorbell ring in the middle of the night and were picked up because of their children.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those are some of the things that happened there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what also happened was that there came the break period where we were in between classes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were out in the schoolyard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody, but nobody played with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was standing there alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And coming from the other school, it was-- it was such a shock and such a trauma for me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was such a trauma for me then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[DRINKS] I had a hard time dealing with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I did not tell my parents about it at home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was ashamed or something.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
